====
BECHAMEL is a full stack application allowing you to create an UML activity diagram where you can add either existing components from the library or your own programmed components.

====
Project launched by Laurent Henocque, Gaetan Janssens(@Petit_Nuage) and Alban Diguer(@albandiguer) in 2009.

